The day before he was hospitalised (May 11), Ivan Semwanga posted on his Facebook page, a video of himself with his 'Rich Gang' team mates at the Blankets and Wine event that took place in Kampala on April 30, 2017.It had been 11 days from the time the 40-year-old was admitted to Steve Biko Academic Hospital in Pretoria South Africa and put on life support machines before his condition deteriorated yesterday morning.